about databene

  <<databene>> hosts a collection of open source libraries and tools
  developed and hosted by {{{./volker_bergmann.html}Volker Bergmann}}. 
  
  Main project is the <<benerator>>, the leading open source test data 
  generator.
  
  
  Core topics of current and future projects are 
  
  * data processing
  
  * software and data quality
  
  * productivity of the development process
  
  * software performance
  
  
 The following libraries and tools are available:
  
*--------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{./databene-benerator/index.html}benerator}}   | a test data generator.                                       |
*--------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{./databene-webdecs/index.html}webdecs}}       | a library for web data extraction, conversion and scripting. |
*--------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+
| {{{./databene-commons/index.html}commons}}       | a library of common utilities and abstractions.              |
*--------------------------------------------------+--------------------------------------------------------------+

